Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.51,0:00:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.47,0:00:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.76,0:00:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.62,0:00:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:49.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:54.95,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:00:56.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:06.77,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.77,0:01:11.82,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever, I take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.46,0:01:24.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it’s not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.72,0:01:30.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.43,0:01:35.55,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard someone else’s biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.55,0:01:37.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn’t there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.36,0:01:44.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.83,0:01:50.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.33,0:01:56.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:02:01.28,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.27,0:02:03.91,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.86,0:02:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.72,0:02:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.87,0:02:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.21,0:02:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.47,0:02:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.38,0:02:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.35,0:02:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.39,0:02:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't take my focus off of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.88,0:02:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what they're going through\Nright now, they'll survive for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I let you get away now,\Nyou'll go kill my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.06,0:03:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't take my focus off of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you really defeat me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't protect anyone unless I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Rifle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Body. Empty Tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was able to meet a man\Nwith some backbone. How disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.11,0:03:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you run out of strength from\Nyour doping earlier after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's backbone you want, I'll show you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...another tactic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Third... Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bone Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.02,0:03:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power that moves\Nfrom one bone to another...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look! My left arm is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.12,0:04:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the arm of a giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's all show, don't even bother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Body!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Giant Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.45,0:04:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shivering Past! Dark Justice and Rob Lucci"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I'm about to pass out.\NI can't fall into the sea like this...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.55,0:05:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and help the injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.50,0:05:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A beast?!\N--No, he's a power holder!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I landed on the deck of\Na battleship. That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He flew from the direction of the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he a pirate?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw a huge hand, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop! I said stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous ahead of here!\NWater is rushing towards us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.63,0:05:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can't you guys hear the sound of water?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, if the water flows into\Nan underground passage like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.04,0:05:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll have no choice but to drown.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro-kun, can't you hear the sound of water?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:06:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, it's true that\Nsomething doesn't feel right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's stop, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other passage. We have\Nno choice but to keep on this path!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny and the others\Nare being chased by water!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Pirate guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.32,0:06:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Do something about this water!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do something?! What're we supposed to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, I told you! This passage is\Ngonna be flooded with water!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nami-san is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...rushing into my arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.42,0:06:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How positive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.44,0:06:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! We're gonna be shut in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't cut it! So this isn't iron or stone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an undersea passage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be made of some damn thick steel\Nthat can bear the water pressure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.99,0:06:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's nowhere to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.22,0:06:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.92,0:06:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't safe here! We're gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:06:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.45,0:07:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no good! The sea train won't start!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't there any engineers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The attacks will reach here soon! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.02,0:07:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do about capturing\NNico Robin on the Bridge of Hesitation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Leave her alone.\N--But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as that man is on this island
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.68,0:07:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and is given the mission\Nof escorting Nico Robin,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.73,0:07:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we don't have to get involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just burn everything down\Nexcept the Bridge of Hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could this man you mentioned be...\NMr. Rob Lucci of CP9?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As we suspected, he's a power holder!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.93,0:07:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're asking who you are! Answer us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:08:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, you idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.68,0:08:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.24,0:08:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put down your guns!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.09,0:08:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you're talking to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.66,0:08:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is... Mr. Rob Lucci of CP9!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Rob Lucci-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.15,0:08:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha... That...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry! Please spare our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.80,0:08:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your mouths. Your whining hurts my ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard a lot about Mr. Rob Lucci,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he is really that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fifteen years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In some kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there was an incident where 500\Nsoldiers got captured by pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:52.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"15 years ago"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Don't hold back! Go wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill anyone who resists! Show no mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't flinch! Protect this\Ncountry from the pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kingdom put up unrelenting\Nresistance against the pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those damn pirates...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trench mortars...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.53,0:09:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it for you! If you don't wanna die,\Njust give up and surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you resist, we'll blow you away\Nwith these trench mortars!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all our hostages!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Throw them all in a warehouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange for the hostages' lives,\Nthe pirate captain demanded the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.31,0:10:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty. For the sake of the citizens,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you should firmly refuse the\Npirates' despicable demand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the power of the kingdom's\Nmain military and the Imperial Guards,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.97,0:10:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we don't have to fear those pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But those soldiers who fought risking their lives
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.03,0:10:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and ended up being taken\Nhostage are also my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just sit back and let them die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.11,0:10:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if this throne is taken away,\Nit's possible to take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't take back people's lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.81,0:10:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if we accepted the pirates' demands,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.99,0:10:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I find it hard to believe that they'd\Nrelease the hostages as they promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty! An emissary from the\NWorld Government has just arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?! From the World Government...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.25,0:11:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show him in immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the kingdom that was about\Nto surrender with its hands tied
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.44,0:11:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,over its concern for the hostages,\Nthe World Government sent a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.48,0:11:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A child?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! That blasted World\NGovernment! How insulting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.95,0:11:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the prey?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.35,0:11:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prey? You mean the pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're occupying the western\Nharbor and making it their hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'd like you to leave the rest to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give the highest priority\Nto the hostages' lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.89,0:12:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to tell the\NWorld Government what to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.48,0:12:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why does this boy make me so intimidated?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The World Government...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.39,0:12:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat and drink to your heart's content\Nand have a good time tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.39,0:12:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A kingdom ain't actually a big deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it ain't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the kingdom will be all ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.42,0:12:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray for the boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.88,0:12:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! He's the new king!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.49,0:12:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.41,0:12:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Booze! We're running out of booze!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Us, too! Someone, bring some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's booze is especially tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You guys...\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's your captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of the World Government,\NI've come to arrest you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrest?! Me?! A brat like you will arrest me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.29,0:13:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like the Government\Nis really hard up for people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can one little brat do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna pretend to be some\Ngovernment big shot, do it somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat it! We got no time\Nto play games with a brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before you get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.97,0:13:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in my way. Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.03,0:13:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you who's gonna move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.48,0:13:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He used a weird technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.64,0:13:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might not be a total lie that\Nyou're from the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you do any more weird stuff,\Nwe can't guarantee the hostages' lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long as you obey us,\Nwe'll keep you alive for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as a hostage for the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.05,0:14:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now no one can defeat us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Throw that brat in the same\Nlockup where the others are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.64,0:14:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have you stay in here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who's that boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a "Great Emissary"\Nfrom the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.43,0:15:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he came to rescue you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.68,0:15:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the Government will\Ndo whatever we tell them to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.49,0:15:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can defeat us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you guys are all hostages.\NTry and get along in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.57,0:15:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to verify one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are all of the hostages here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.26,0:15:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shave!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tempest Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the boy infiltrated the\Npirates' hideout, right then and there,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he killed all 500 of the kingdom's\Nsoldiers who were taken hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Killed all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be...! Is something like that permissible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.77,0:16:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's the World Government...\NEven if it's for justice...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:21.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Justice"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up. Justice isn't all warm and fuzzy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, too, remember it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.22,0:16:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, the pirates got\Nangry and rained bullets
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,upon the boy who was standing on the\Nmountain of bodies with his back turned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the boy stood up in the flame of explosions,\Nkilled the boss of the pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and settled that incident all by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! Boss! Boss!...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.68,0:16:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pipe down! What's the problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.41,0:16:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That brat is going on a rampage in the lockup!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.98,0:16:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.59,0:17:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you... kill our important hostages...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They committed a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.64,0:17:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I executed them in the name of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.52,0:17:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.99,0:17:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soldiers of the kingdom,\Nbeing weak is a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They surrendered to evil and\Nplunged the kingdom into a crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.71,0:17:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soldiers like that don't have the right to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They deserve to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! And you call yourself\Nan official of the World Government?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Justice would never surrender to evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Bring him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That serves you right, you damn brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't treat us like fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! After all the trouble we\Nwent through, our plan got ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H... How could he have survived that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shave!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.47,0:18:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finger Pistol.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boy, who had several\Nbullet marks on his back,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was a CP9 intelligence agent at the age of 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.58,0:18:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People call him the strongest\Nand cruelest mass killing machine
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.78,0:18:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the history of CP9,\Nwhose mission is dark justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that he was capable of\Nall that when he was only 13...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.45,0:18:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly why all we have\Nto do is fulfill our own duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something came out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Straw Hat Luffy, whose\Nbounty is 100 million Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.47,0:19:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think he'd be that fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are! Pigeon guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.98,0:19:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't work! The Bone Balloon is tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum... Giant Axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.70,0:19:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?! Is it a giant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum... Giant Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.78,0:20:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.59,0:20:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The masts got broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're falling down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fight between those two is just crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.52,0:20:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finger Pistol...! Pick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.12,0:20:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that as your power increases,\Nyour speed decreases.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tempest Kick... Victory Bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.76,0:20:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The iron outer shell got cracked...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ship won't last long!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.39,0:21:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close. I almost got split in two.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.75,0:21:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that, Cutty Flam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over for you guys! Or rather,\Nit was all over from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.18,0:21:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit early to say that\Nwhen the fight isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who is fighting Straw Hat is Lucci.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.42,0:21:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the strongest man in the history of CP9!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.75,0:21:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might've been able to\Nget rid of the others okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.15,0:21:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Lucci's another story entirely!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.92,0:21:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once Straw Hat is taken out,\Nyou're next, Cutty Flam!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.49,0:21:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? Give me a report.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.77,0:21:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir, Vice Admiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.58,0:21:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We heard that Straw Hat Luffy and\NMr. Rob Lucci of CP9 are currently fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.04,0:21:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, the #4 ship got wrecked!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.42,0:21:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rob Lucci isn't gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the gunners on all ships, aim at the #4 ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.09,0:21:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire all cannons together in five seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.87,0:21:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha... Vice Admiral, you must be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.41,0:22:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One thousand of our men are onboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.72,0:22:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A moment's indecision can allow\Nvicious criminals to slip away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.64,0:22:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you protect our future from them?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.95,0:22:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.04,0:22:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were finally able to free Robin-chan,\Nbut if we don't do anything, we'll drown!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.34,0:22:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't breathe... I can't hold my breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.49,0:22:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Am I dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:22:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How beautiful... you are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.01,0:23:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.52,0:23:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Mystical Mermaid Appears?\NAs Consciousness Fades Away..."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.27,0:23:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
